.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, black, ivory, lavender
1. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
3. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the person who likes black and the person who likes ivory##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Color   | ivory | chestnut | lavender | black |

