.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, time-travel, scientific
1. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching mystery movies##7
4. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | thriller | scientific | time-travel |

